              li: a(class= "link" href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCrqAGUPPMOdo0jfQ6grikZw") colt Steele  
              li: a(class= "link" href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCO1cgjhGzsSYb1rsB4bFe4Q") Fun Fun Function 
              li: a(class= "link" href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCqrILQNl5Ed9Dz6CGMyvMTQ") Clever Programmer
              li: a(class= "link" href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC29ju8bIPH5as8OGnQzwJyA") Traversy Media 
          p 
            |I also actively listen to podcasts(<a class= "link" href="https://syntax.fm/">Syntax</a>, <a class= "link" href="https://www.codenewbie.org/">Codenewbie</a>, <a class= "link" href="https://shoptalkshow.com/">Shoptalk</a>, <a class= "link" href="https://www.redhat.com/en/command-line-heroes">Command_Line Heroes</a> and <a class= "link" href="https://www.indiehackers.com/">Indie Hackers</a>) and read articles on various topics or visiting local meetups. Maybe one day I will become a JavaScript wizard. A man can dream...
          
          p
            | When I'm not doing something IT related I like to spend time with my amazing wife Madoka, traveling around Japan to see all of the beautiful temples and scenery, exercising, cooking, becoming a Kanji(漢字) master, playing foot-golf with the boys, and attempting to try all the craft beer in the world(I think I am about half-way there by now..) 
          
          
